## Dependencies & Building

* SDL
* SDL_ttf
* SDL_image
* SDL_mixer

To compile FreeBlocks, simply run `cmake . && make` in the base directory.



## Controls

* Arrow keys / Joystick D-pad = Move cursor
* Z / Joystick Button 0 = Switch blocks / Confirm menu selection
* X / Joystick Button 1 = Manually bump up the stack / Go to previous menu
* ESC / Joystick Button 9 = Pause the game / Exit the game when on the title screen

## Controls (GCW-Zero)

* D-Pad = Move cursor
* A = Switch blocks / Confirm menu selection
* B = Manually bump up the stack / Go to previous menu
* Start = Pause the game
* Select = Exit the game when on the title screen

